   FORMÁLNÍ DOPIS V AJ : Pomoc prosím.
   Dobrý den,

   určitě zde jsou někteří skvělí angličtináři, kteří posoudí, zda je to
   dobré. Chci vědět zda jsou tam odpovídající formální výrazy, správné časy
   a podobně. Děkuji

   Dear Mr. Adams

   I am writing to complain about the cellular phone called Apple Iphone SE
   which I bought in your on-line shop one month ago.

   I am not satisfied with the product and service you offer. There are the
   specific reasons. Firstly, you state on your website that the maximum
   delivery time for the shipment is five days. Nonetheless, I was waiting
   for three weeks. In other words, this is almost four times longer time
   than you declare.

   Secondly, your advertisement promised that if there were any problems,
   they would be resolved very quickly and willingly by your employees. In
   my case, it was a completely different reality. The phone broke down
   after just three days of use. I decided to call your company. The staff
   were not pleasant at all. Moreover, they do not seem to understand much
   about the issue. Ultimately, their advice have been unnecesary. The phone
   is still not working.

   I am of the opinion that choosing and communication your on-line shop has
   been total waste of both my time and money. Therefore, I demand a
   complete refund the cellular phone, including postage and packing.

   Yours Sincerely,
   xx
