Dear Mr. Adams,

I am writing to complain about the cellular phone Apple Iphone SE which I
purchased from your online shop one month ago.

I am not satisfied with the product and services you offer. To substantiate
this claim, I am going to give specific reasons. Firstly, you state on your
website that the maximum delivery time for the shipment is five days. However,
I was had to wait for three weeks. In other words, this period is almost four
times longer than you declare.

Secondly, your advertisement promised that should there be any problems, these
would be resolved promptly and willingly by your employees. Unfortunately,
this was not the case. The phone broke down after just three days of use. I
decided to call your company. The staff were not pleasant at all. Moreover,
they did not seem to understand the issue very well. Ultimately, their advice
was of little help. The phone is still not working.

I am now convinced that choosing your online shop and communication with your
company was sheer waste of both my time and money. Therefore, I demand a
complete refund for the cellular phone, including postage and packing
expenses.

Yours sincerely,
[Smajlík]
